'''矽化鈉'''（NaSi, Na2Si, Na4Si4）是坚硬的黑色或灰色结晶材料。<ref name="MSDS">[http://signachem.com/wp-content/themes/signa/pdf/technical-docs/MSDS-SiGNa%20NaSi.pdf Material Safety Data Sheet, SiGNa Chemistry, Inc.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120127230037/http://signachem.com/wp-content/themes/signa/pdf/technical-docs/MSDS-SiGNa%20NaSi.pdf |date=2012-01-27 }}</ref>

矽化鈉与水反应产生气态[[氢|氢]]和[[硅酸钠|硅酸钠]]。这是个[[放热反应|放热反应]](~175 kJ/mol)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2006/07/hydrogen_produc.html |title=Hydrogen Production from Sodium Silicide Powder; Prospects for On-Board Generation, 14 July 2006 |accessdate=2013-09-14 |archive-date=2013-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130709152345/http://www.greencarcongress.com/2006/07/hydrogen_produc.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
: 2 NaSi + 5 H<sub>2</sub>O → 5 H<sub>2</sub> + Na<sub>2</sub>Si<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub>

在氢技术，该反应用来产生[[氢气|氢气]]。

